\begin{equation}
\nabla^2 h_{\mu\nu} \cdot \Psi_{\text{solar}} = \lambda_n \Psi_{\text{solar}}
\end{equation}
where $\lambda_n$ are eigenvalues satisfying the helical boundary conditions:
\begin{equation}
\lambda_n = -\left(\frac{n\pi}{L}\right)^2 + i\frac{\Omega_{\text{sun}}}{v_{sw}}
\end{equation}
